&lt;p&gt;  I can confirm in last revision 1711465 sessions are correctly closed.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;  Thanks for fixing.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Tomas&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
